      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>LTF 新疆葵花籽（30g 小包装）</title>\n<style>\n  body {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    background-color: #F4F4F5;\n    margin: 0; padding: 0;\n  }\n  header {\n    background-color: #FF4D4F;\n    color: #fff;\n    padding: 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  main {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: auto;\n    padding: 20px;\n    gap: 20px;\n  }\n  section {\n    background: #fff;\n    padding: 15px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n  }\n  #product-info-section {\n    flex: 1 1 45%;\n  }\n  #product-info-section img {\n    max-width: 100%;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n  }\n  #price-info-section {\n    flex: 1 1 45%;\n    border: 2px solid #FFD666;\n  }\n  #price-info-section h2 {\n    color: #FF4D4F;\n  }\n  #buy-flow-section {\n    flex: 1 1 100%;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  button {\n    background-color: #FF4D4F;\n    color: #fff;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 10px 20px;\n    margin: 5px;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n  }\n  button:hover {\n    background-color: #d9363e;\n  }\n  #promotion-tags-section span {\n    background-color: #FFD666;\n    padding: 5px 10px;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    margin-right: 10px;\n  }\n  #user-interactions-section {\n    flex: 1 1 100%;\n  }\n  .stars {\n    cursor: pointer;\n    color: #FFD666;\n    font-size: 20px;\n  }\n  .comment-list {\n    margin-top: 10px;\n    border-top: 1px solid #ccc;\n    padding-top: 10px;\n  }\n  .comment-item {\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;\n    padding: 5px 0;\n  }\n  #customer-service-section {\n    flex: 1 1 100%;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  #recommended-products-section {\n    flex: 1 1 100%;\n  }\n  .product-card {\n    display: inline-block;\n    width: 200px;\n    margin: 10px;\n    text-align: center;\n    border: 1px solid #ddd;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .product-card img {\n    max-width: 100%;\n  }\n  .product-card h4 {\n    background-color: #F4F4F5;\n    padding: 5px;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<header>\n  <h1>LTF 新疆葵花籽（30g 小包装）</h1>\n</header>\n<main>\n  <section id=\"product-info-section\">\n    <h1>品牌 LTF 新疆葵花籽（30g 小包装）</h1>\n    <p>来自新疆的优质葵花籽，小包装方便携带，30g 每包，精选原料，香脆可口，健康零食好选择。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300?text=%E8%91%B5%E8%8A%B1%E7%B1%BD\" alt=\"新疆葵花籽外观图\">\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"price-info-section\">\n    <h2>现价：￥16.9（10 包）</h2>\n    <p>原价：￥19.9，限时优惠立减 <strong>3 元</strong>！</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"buy-flow-section\">\n    <button onclick=\"buyNow()\">立即购买</button>\n    <button onclick=\"addToCart()\">加入购物车</button>\n    <p>购物流程：选择数量 → 点击购买按钮 → 进入支付页面 → 完成付款。</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"promotion-tags-section\">\n    <span>限时促销</span>\n    <p>库存剩余 120 件，快抢购！</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"user-interactions-section\">\n    <div id=\"rating\">\n      评分：\n      <span class=\"stars\" onclick=\"rate(1)\">★</span>\n      <span class=\"stars\" onclick=\"rate(2)\">★</span>\n      <span class=\"stars\" onclick=\"rate(3)\">★</span>\n      <span class=\"stars\" onclick=\"rate(4)\">★</span>\n      <span class=\"stars\" onclick=\"rate(5)\">★</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"comment-list\" id=\"comments\">\n      <div class=\"comment-item\">用户A：很香，很好吃！</div>\n    </div>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"commentInput\" placeholder=\"发表您的评论\">\n    <button onclick=\"addComment()\">提交评论</button>\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"customer-service-section\">\n    <button onclick=\"contactService()\">联系客服</button>\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"recommended-products-section\">\n    <h3>推荐商品</h3>\n    <div class=\"product-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150?text=%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%B1%BD%E7%B1%BD\" alt=\"推荐商品\">\n      <h4>LTF 黑瓜子 200g</h4>\n      <p>￥12.9</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"product-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150?text=%E5%A5%97%E8%A3%85%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\" alt=\"组合套装\">\n      <h4>坚果组合礼包</h4>\n      <p>￥35.0</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</main>\n<script>\nfunction buyNow(){\n  alert(\"跳转到支付页面\");\n}\nfunction addToCart(){\n  alert(\"商品已加入购物车\");\n}\nfunction rate(stars){\n  alert(\"您评分了：\" + stars + \" 星\");\n}\nfunction addComment(){\n  var input = document.getElementById(\"commentInput\");\n  if(input.value.trim() !== \"\"){\n    var commentList = document.getElementById(\"comments\");\n    var newComment = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    newComment.className = \"comment-item\";\n    newComment.textContent = \"用户：\" + input.value;\n    commentList.appendChild(newComment);\n    input.value = \"\";\n  }\n}\nfunction contactService(){\n  alert(\"正在为您连接客服...\");\n}\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
